  "title": "Shrinking the Future: 'LL",
  "learningGoal": "The learner will fluidly vocalize cliticized pronoun-modal contractions (I'll, He'll, They'll) reducing the two-syllable phrase into a single smooth phonologic slide, enhancing conversational flow.",
